title: The Hellacopters - Live at Hultsfred Festival (12.06.1997).avi
description:
The Hellacopters
Live at Hultsfred festival, Sweden
June 12, 1997

I&#039;m not exactly sure if this actually is from Hultsfred, because someone once told me different. 
Anyways, the thing that matters is that this is a brilliant show by The Hellacopters (like always). Just look at the setlist:

01. (Gotta Get Some Action) NOW!
02. Fake Baby
03. Born Broke
04. You Are Nothin&#039;
05. Ferrytale
06. Random Riot
07. 1995
08. My Mephistophelean Creed
09. Misanthropic High
10. Soulseller
11. Ghoul School
12. Another Place
13. Tilt City


It&#039;s not a Pro-shot video, but decent quality and shot from the side of the stage. That should be enough if you just like the band. You can naturally look at the videos on Youtube.

AND please support them by buying those great releases (there are no lemons) and going to the gigs - there&#039;s not many left unfortunately.

Enjoy!!
